      "content": "i get that, but im kinda wary of doctors because they always just want to run dozens of expensive tests and tell u to take tiny amounts that dont actually do anything. i've seen a lot of wellness biohackers on youtube who swear by the high dose method to basically \"reset\" their system. do you really think it's that much of a risk for just a few weeks? it's not like im taking it forever.",
